query:
SELECT
                  tt.id as "id!: Uuid",
                  tt.tag_id as "tag_id!: Uuid",
                  t.tag_name as "tag_name!",
                  t.content as "content!",
                  t.color as "color?",
                  tt.created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
               FROM task_tags tt
               JOIN tags t ON t.id = tt.tag_id
               WHERE tt.task_id = $1
               ORDER BY t.tag_name ASC
